# Fix Node 20 Deprecation Warnings in GitHub Actions

## Problem
13 warnings on CI run https://github.com/getsentry/cli/actions/runs/23457533348 — all are "Node.js 20 actions are deprecated". GitHub will force Node.js 24 starting June 2, 2026.

## Unique Deprecated Actions (from warnings)

| Action | Current Version | Upgrade To | Node Runtime |
|--------|----------------|------------|-------------|
| `actions/checkout` | `@v4` (10 places in ci.yml, generate-skill.yml, docs-preview.yml) | `@v6` | node24 |
| `actions/cache` | `@v4` (7 places) | `@v5` | node24 |
| `actions/upload-artifact` | `@v4` (4 places) | `@v7` | node24 |
| `actions/download-artifact` | `@v4` (3 places) | `@v8` | node24 |
| `actions/setup-node` | `@v4` (2 places) | `@v6` | node24 |
| `actions/create-github-app-token` | `@v2.2.1` (2 places) | `@v3` | node24 |
| `dorny/paths-filter` | SHA `de90cc6...` (v3.0.2) | `@v4` | node24 |
| `getsentry/codecov-action` | `@main` | **Cannot fix here** — the action itself uses `node20` in its `action.yml` | node20 |

## Notes
- `release.yml` already uses `actions/checkout@v6` — no change needed there
- `oven-sh/setup-bun@v2` already resolves to v2.2.0 with node24 — no change needed
- `rossjrw/pr-preview-action@v1` is a composite action (shell-based) — no Node runtime concern
- `getsentry/codecov-action@main` uses `node20` in its own `action.yml` — needs a fix in that separate repo, not here
- `changelog-preview.yml` uses a reusable workflow from `getsentry/craft` — no direct action references to update

