## Breaking Changes Review

- **`actions/upload-artifact@v7`**: Adds `archive` input (default `true`). Our usage doesn't set it, so behavior is unchanged.
- **`actions/download-artifact@v8`**: Defaults `digest-mismatch` to `error`. This is stricter but desirable for our CI (catches corrupted artifacts).
- **`actions/create-github-app-token@v3`**: Requires Runner v2.327.1+. GitHub-hosted runners already meet this.
- **`dorny/paths-filter@v4`**: Node 24 upgrade, no input changes.
- **`actions/setup-node@v6`**: Limits automatic caching to npm only (breaking from v5 which added auto-cache for all managers). We don't use automatic caching — we use `actions/cache` separately.

## Fix: Revert AGENTS.md

The cherry-pick resolved the AGENTS.md conflict with `--theirs`, which replaced the current lore-managed content with an older version. This needs to be reverted.

Steps:
1. Restore AGENTS.md to the version from `origin/main` (HEAD~1)
2. Amend the commit to exclude AGENTS.md changes
3. Force-push

